h3. Problem Definition
The attachment directory structure has been changed since JIRA 7.0.0. However, there's no documentation explaining more about the new structure.

For example,
JIRA 6.4 stored attachments in : {{$JIRA_Home/data/jira/data/attachments/PROJECT_KEY/ISSUE_KEY/ID}}
JIRA 7.2 stores attachments in : {{$JIRA_Home/data/jira/data/attachments/PROJECT_KEY/x0000/ISSUE_KEY/ID}}

h3. Suggestion
Please create a documentation to explain about the new attachment directory structure

